{
  "id": "adv_event_2110_01_06",
  "title": "宴を終えて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "それではみなさん、ライブお疲れ様！\nそれと～……はい、琴乃ちゃん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good show‚ everyone!\nAnd… you’re up‚ Kotono-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、私！？　え、えっと……こほん\nお姉ちゃん、お誕生日おめでとう。乾杯",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ me!? I‚ erm‚ ahem…\nOnee-chan‚ happy birthday! Cheers!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.733333333333333,
      "endTime": 21.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "かんぱーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cheers!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5,
      "endTime": 23.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（寮に戻り、打ち上げを兼ねた麻奈の）\n（バースデーパーティーを行なったんだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We went back to the dorm for an after-show party)\n(and Mana’s birthday party.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.933333333333337,
      "endTime": 31.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "すぅ……すぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Zzz… zzz…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.433333333333337,
      "endTime": 38.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ～ん……もう一杯くらいいいでしょ～……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huhhh… C’mon‚ just one more cup of…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7,
      "endTime": 44.833333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな寝てしまうとは……よっぽど疲れてたんだな\nまあ、それもそうか……長い一日だったもんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re all asleep‚ so they must have been really tired.\nWell‚ it has been a really long day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 56.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……麻奈はにぎやかなのが好きだったもんな\nきっと、喜んでくれるよな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Mana did like things to be lively‚ after all.\nI’m sure she’s delighted…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.43333333333333,
      "endTime": 64.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……俺も、前に進んでいくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m moving forward too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 69.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ……\nあ、{user}さん、起きてたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*yawn*\nOh‚ {user}-san‚ you’re still up?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4,
      "endTime": 80.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "……うぅん、今何時ですかぁ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nnph… What time is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 85.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "さくら、こころ。もう少し寝てても大丈夫だぞ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ Kokoro‚ you can sleep a bit longer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 90.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですよ。ちょっとだけ後片付けしちゃいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s fine. I’m just going to tidy up a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 95.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "しばらく寝れそうにないですし\nしょうがないので手伝いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t think I’ll be able to sleep for a while‚\nso I may as well lend a hand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4,
      "endTime": 100.60000000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "あーもう、みんなお腹を冷やしちゃいますよ\nサービスで私が毛布をかけてあげます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re all going to catch a cold.\nI’ll cover them with blankets.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.83333333333333,
      "endTime": 107.39999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんってばこんな無防備な格好で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh Rio-san‚ you’re so defenseless…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 112.16666666666669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんに\n襲われたらどうするんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What would you do if {user}-san\nwere to make inappropriate advances?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 115.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "こころは俺をなんだと思ってるんだ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What does Kokoro think I am…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.6,
      "endTime": 118.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ。……莉央さんは寒さ対策のトレーニング\nということで、毛布は薄手でいいですかね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nevermind~…… I’ll give her a thinner blanket\nto train her to cope with the cold.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 129.7333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "素直じゃないんだから\nさりげなく毛布を重ねがけしてるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t mean that.\nYou’re piling on more blankets for her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 134.89999999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "……これは筋トレの一種ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….This is a kind of strength training.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3,
      "endTime": 138.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "こころちゃんって……すっごく可愛いね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re always so cute‚ Kokoro-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.86666666666667,
      "endTime": 143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "くっ……そんなキラキラした目で言われると\nすっごくやり辛いです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You saying it with…those shining stars in your eyes‚\njust makes it harder to hear…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.2,
      "endTime": 149.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "はは、思わぬ天敵が現れたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ looks like you met your unexpected match.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3,
      "endTime": 153.63333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "……ほら、早く片付けちゃいましょう\n{user}さんも手伝って下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Come on now‚ let’s clear up quickly.\nYou too‚ {user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.9,
      "endTime": 158.76666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "まったくもー\n今日はブラック企業な一日でしたよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really…\nToday was a day of unpaid overtime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 165.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、パーティーとライブの準備も\n私達でしたんだもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha. We did the preparations\nfor the party and the show!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.26666666666668,
      "endTime": 170.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "全部突然だったのに、付き合ってくれて\nありがとうね、こころちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even when it was all so sudden.\nthanks for helping‚ Kokoro-chan‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 175.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "別にいいですよ。麻奈さんに興味も湧きましたし\n……今度、ブルーレイとか貸してくれたりします？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s fine. It aroused my interest in Mana-san.\n…Would you lend me a Blu-ray disk of her next time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 185.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06/sud_vo_adv_event_2110_01_06-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、いくらでも貸すよ\n一緒に観よっか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ as many as you like.\nWe could watch them together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.6,
      "endTime": 190.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
